8/25/literature/","excerpt":"","text":"值得收藏的文艺语句​ “可是这假意浪漫的万物中，只有你才是我所要描摹的真身。” “城市的夜空只有月亮。想你的时候，把湖面的镜子敲碎，让星星一颗、一颗浮上来。” “没有你，我的时间是缓慢的米勒行星”","categories":[{"name":"articles","slug":"articles","permalink":"http://weiweii.top/categories/articles/"}],"tags":[],"author":"ww"},{"title":"Hello World","slug":"hello-world","date":"2020-08-25T08:56:31.447Z","updated":"2020-08-25T09:27:52.948Z","comments":true,"path":"2020/08/25/hello-world/","link":"","permalink":"http://weiweii.top/2020/08/25/hello-world/","excerpt":"","text":"Welcome to Hexo! This is your very first post. Check documentation for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in troubleshooting or you can ask me on GitHub. Quick StartCreate a new post1$ hexo new &quot;My New Post&quot; More info: Writing Run server1$ hexo server More info: Server Generate static files1$ hexo generate More info: Generating Deploy to remote sites1$ hexo deploy More info: Deployment","categories":[],"tags":[],"author":"ww"}],"categories":[{"name":"tools","slug":"tools","permalink":"http://weiweii.top/categories/tools/"},{"name":"articles","slug":"articles","permalink":"http://weiweii.top/categories/articles/"}],"tags":[]}